# Keybindings

## Playback
bind space toggle-play
bind a add
bind A add-to
bind ] next
bind [ prev
bind } next-of albumartist
bind { prev-of albumartist
bind > next-of album
bind < prev-of album
bind h seek -3
bind l seek 3
bind H seek -10
bind L seek 10
bind = volume +3
bind - volume -3
bind m mute
bind r repeat
bind z random
bind s single

## Adding & Playing
bind b add-album
bind B play-album
# bind r remove

## Playlist management
bind R clear
bind S shuffle
bind J move 1
bind K move -1
bind v toggle-select
bind V clear-selection

## Application
bind I info
bind ? help
bind : command-mode
bind ; command-mode
bind tab next-window
bind ` last-window
bind ^L redraw
bind q quit

## Movement & Search
bind j move-down
bind k move-up
bind d move-halfpgdn
bind u move-halfpgup
bind ^F move-pgdn
bind ^B move-pgup
bind g move-home
bind G move-end
bind c goto-current
bind f filter
bind F clear-filters
bind / quick-find
bind n next-result
bind N prev-result

bind y ! echo "#" | xsel
bind ^T ! transcribe "#"
bind ^W ! lyrics | less

